{"tid":2449643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普呼籲所有支持者接種疫苗：疫苗安全有效 連登仔仲打唔打？","createTime":"2021-03-17T00:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T16:36:55.000Z","uid":391580,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5757880435c0a2cc4daf5cf98d14550436561fee","tid":2449643,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:07:15.000Z","msg":"週二(3月16日)，美國前總統特朗普(Donald J. Trump)與瑪利亞&middot;巴蒂羅姆(Maria Bartiromo)在《福克斯新聞黃金時間》(Fox News Primetime)獨家亮相。<br />\n<br />\n在採訪中，巴蒂羅姆問這位前總統是否會建議他的支持者自願接種新冠病毒疫苗，她指出，相當多的共和黨人仍然感到不安或反對在這個時候接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我會的，&rdquo;特朗普回應道。 &ldquo;我會推薦它，我會推薦給很多不想接種它的人，坦率地說，其中很多人投票給了我。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;但是，我們有我們的自由，我們必須遵守自由，我也同意這一點。但這是一種很好的疫苗。這是一種安全的疫苗，而且有效。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，製藥公司和美國食品和藥品管理局(FDA)一直在&ldquo;夜以繼日&rdquo;地開發各種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F3pJLR1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF3pJLR1.png&h=aa039cc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3792db93c5fc671aeb568fd5649623e68420281a","tid":2449643,"uid":391580,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:08:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔：疫苗唔安全<br />\n我打算十年之後再打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27880f82beb9a243f8aa4557b7e30a231d4d9d75","tid":2449643,"uid":228894,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:09:44.000Z","msg":"只要唔係支那疫苗<br />\n就唔排除打嘅可能性"},{"pid":"cf967f88d0fcd21e0861392f547a42e55cfa9dea","tid":2449643,"uid":58841,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:11:00.000Z","msg":"我睇左幾次你係咪無常識<br />\n美國係真係美國貨<br />\n香港啲全部支那野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4338ae9c6ae3f11bbd9ed8c4e0e78cd26c6c5e66","tid":2449643,"uid":391580,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cf967f88d0fcd21e0861392f547a42e55cfa9dea","tid":2449643,"uid":58841,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:11:00.000Z","msg